    "en":
        "Quarantine is done for the larger interest of the community but it can lead to physical, psychological, emotional and financial stress due to fear of contracting the illness, boredom, loneliness, loss of personal freedom, a new set of daily routine and lack of social togetherness. Signs that someone is experiencing serious distress include",
    "hi":
